<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pago Cancelado - IAMOVING</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .cancel-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid #dc3545;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .cancel-icon::before,
        .cancel-icon::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 40px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: #dc3545;
        }
        .cancel-icon::before {
            transform: rotate(45deg);
        }
        .cancel-icon::after {
            transform: rotate(-45deg);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="card shadow">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <div class="cancel-icon mb-4"></div>
                        <h2 class="card-title mb-4">Pago Cancelado</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">Lo sentimos, tu pago ha sido cancelado.</p>
                        <p class="card-text">Por favor, vuelve a intentar realizar el pago.</p>
                        <p class="card-text mt-4">
                            <strong>Número de referencia:</strong> 
                            <span class="badge bg-secondary">{{ $consulta->id }}</span>
                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <!--<a href="{{ route('iamovingtospain.reintentar.pago', ['consulta_id' => $consulta->id]) }}" class="btn btn-primary me-2">Reintentar Pago</a>
                            <a href="" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Volver a la página principal</a>-->
                            <a href="/iamoving-to-spain#agendarConsulta" class="btn btn-primary me-2">Reintentar Pago</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>